Package frog.entities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Entity
    Represents an abstract entity which all other entities will extend, detects collisions using awt rectangles.
    Fly
    Represents a lower level fly monster that extends the Monster class.
    Frog
    Represents a frog that extends Entity.
    Monster
    A monster class where all monsters extend this class.
    Shopkeeper
    Represents a shopkeeper which you can interact with to bring up a shop GUI.
    Snake
    Represents a higher level snake monster that extends the Monster class.
    Sorcerer
    Represents the Sorcerer final boss.
